Posts.Content: Jan 31, 2013 08:49AM spincera wrote: I'm getting my biopsy today. I got up early because I couldn't sleep. My biopsy is this afternoon. I'm a student, so since I found out the news, I haven't really been able to do any school work. My mind has been in a fog, and my emotions have been on a rollercoaster. I can relate. I hope everyone gets good news when you get your results. It's definitely been tough to go through. Best wishes!!
